Using Div to make Blocks:  

 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>HTML Blocks Application</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h3>HTML Blocks Application</h3>
        <div style="color: #ff00ff">
            <p>1st group: Some Premiership Teams</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Arsenal FC</li>
                <li>Leicester FC</li>
                <li>Manchester FC</li>
                <li>Man United</li>
                <li>Chelsea FC</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="color: #808080">
            <p>2nd group: Some Food Types</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Burger</li>
                <li>Cheese</li>
                <li>Vegetables</li>
                <li>Bread</li>
                <li>Sandwich</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>

Using Span to make Blocks:

   <body>
        <h3>HTML Blocks Application</h3>
        <p>Hello <span style="color: #ff00ff">YouTubers</span> and welcome to <span style="color: #800080">software developer</span> channel.</p>
    </body>
